This is a source code for http://perlresume.org.

How to install

1. Clone the repository

    git clone http://github.com/vti/perlresume.org

2. Install dependencies

    cpanm --installdeps .

3. Setup SQLite database

    sqlite3 perlresume.db < schema/*.sql

4. Start the embedded server

    plackup bin/app.pl
